name: Florence Welch Red
description:
Florence Welch Red - By Richard Koscher - https://www.richardkoscherart.com/

Florence's lyrics have always touched me on a very deep level, combined with what I think is THE best female voice of all times, there is not a more favorite artist of mine that I can think of. I have seen Florence + the Machine now three times in concert, once with my daughter (which was her first concert) Florence, if you ever read this - We were a family pulled from a flood.
